nail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FF9QYvP&h=929132e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1994 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKBU 香港浸會大學 (Hong Kong Baptist University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/aFkVTK\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FaFkVTK&h=c02dba86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1991 年</span></span>：<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKUST 香港科技大學 (The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology)</span></span> 成立<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/LEAwFT\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FLEAwFT&h=887bebfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1949 年：<ins>新亞書院 New Asia College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/WxZn5K\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FWxZn5K&h=4f2e374a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1951 年：<ins>崇基學院 Chung Chi College</ins>（由民國大陸時期十三間基督教大學遷到香港組成）<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/ZKUm8U\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZKUm8U&h=8da962d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1956 年：<ins>聯合書院 United College of Hong Kong</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/bcNSdS\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FbcNSdS&h=b1f2aa0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1963 年</span></span>：三院合併，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">CUHK 香港中文大學 (The Chinese University of Hong Kong)</span></span> 成立<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/p3ptNx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fp3ptNx&h=7855c725&s=